            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo nono, ipsa die kal. ianuarii,
                        indictione septima. Manifesti sumus nos <persName ref="#people/3214"
                            >Ubertus</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3216"
                            >Sesmundi</persName> et <persName ref="#people/3226"
                            >Castracane</persName> eius filius et <persName ref="#people/3233"
                            >Sindica</persName> uxor suprascripti Uberti et quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Alferius">Alferii</name></persName> filia quia communiter et
                        consentiente mihi qui supra Castracane suprascripto patre meo (…) ubi
                        interesse videtur notitia <persName><name ref="Widaloctus"
                            >Guidalotti</name></persName> (…) Sindice fratris et suprascripti
                        Castracani (…) per hanc cartulam damus et tradimus iure pingnoris et
                        hypothece tibi <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidoni</name></persName> dei
                            gratia<orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Churches #Hospitals">
                            <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> et <rs key="#Hospitals"
                                >hospitalis</rs> Sancti Iacobi de <placeName ref="#places/3207"
                                key="#Churches #Hospitals">Altopascio</placeName></orgName> rectori
                        reverendo (…) duarum <rs key="#Petiae">petiarum</rs> terrarum in integrum
                        que sunt posita loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Rivers #Petiae #Castle #Roads">Potho</placeName>, iuxta <rs
                            key="#Rivers">flumen quod dicitur Giusciana</rs>. Una quarum est dicta
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210">Campo del Vignale</placeName> et tenet
                        unum caput et latum in predicto flumine Giusciane et in rio, aliud caput in
                        terra filiorum quondam <persName ref="#people/3232">Eppi</persName>, aliud
                        latus in terra suprascripti hospitalis qui ei obvenit a quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3215">Passavante</persName> iure iudicati. Et est ipsa
                        petia per mensuram ad iustam seminaturam stariora novem et si amplius est.
                        Altera est dicta <placeName ref="#places/3210">Campo del
                        Pratale</placeName>, et tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via
                            publica</rs>, aliud caput in terra <persName><name ref="Gherardus"
                                >Gherardini</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lambertucci</name></persName> et aliquantulum in
                        terra nostra, latus in terra suprascripti hospitalis, qui ei obvenit iure
                        iudicati a quondam suprascripto Passavante, aliud latus in terra nostra qui
                        supra iugales, ubi fossa est in medio. Et est ipsa petia per mensuram ad
                        iustam seminaturam stariora duodecim et si plus est. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: libris viginti (…) tali videlicet tenore quod
                        si a proximiori festivitate omnium sanctorum preterita usque ad duos annos
                        proxime venturos (…) solverimus soldos duocentum bonorum denariorum (…)
                        supra primo notatum petium terre vobis pignoris et hypothece iure (…) et
                        duocentum alios soldos bonorum denariorum (…) pro quibus alterum supra
                        notatum petium terre vobis obligavimus, cartula ista sit inane et vacuum
                        (sic) et in nostra revertatur potestate. (…) Si non solverimus exinde
                        habeatis et teneatis (…) predicta petia terrarum cum usu et fructibus. (…)
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign> in duplum (…) et insuper libras viginti argenti
                        optimi nomine pene. Et in tali ordine hec scribere <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Gunduinus">Guntulinum</name></persName>
                        apostolice sedis <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notarium</rs> rogavimus. Acta
                        sunt hec in <rs key="#Castle">castello</rs> de suprascripto Pottho in curia
                        suprascriptorum iugalium. (…) <persName key="#Witness #Other_clerics"><name
                                ref="Petrus">Petri</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_clerics">cappellanus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3213"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ecclesie</rs> de <placeName ref="#places/3231" key="#Churches"
                                >Lignano</placeName></orgName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Farulfus de San Miniato">Farolfus</name></persName>
                        <persName><name ref="Zaccarellus">Zaccarelli</name></persName> filius de
                            <placeName ref="#places/730">San Miniato</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Francardinus">Francardinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Brunectus de Cerbaia">Brunetti</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/3208">Cerbaia</placeName></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Alcheruolus"
                            >Alcherolii</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes Sepi">Iohannis Sepi</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ambrosius">Ambrosini</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Rainuccius">Ranuccini</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Carus/Strambus">Carone
                                Strambi</name></persName> magistro discipulus his interfuerunt et
                        rogati sunt <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (S) Ego Guntulinus apostolice
                        sedis notarium post traditam complevi et dedi.</ab>
